ratePage-vote-error: Error message displayed upon voting failure
ratePage-vote-title: Main label of the rating widget
ratePage-vote-info: Label informing the user on how they voted on a specific page. $1 is the rating's value (a natural number, most often single-digit).
ratePage-vote-average-info: Label showing the average rating for the page and the number of votes the have been cast.
ratePage-caption-1: Title of the worst rating shown when hovering over it with the cursor
ratePage-caption-2: Title of the second worst rating shown when hovering over it with the cursor
ratePage-caption-3:
Title of the middle rating shown when hovering over it with the cursor
{{identical|OK}}
ratePage-caption-4:
Title of the second best rating shown when hovering over it with the cursor
{{identical|Good}}
ratePage-caption-5: Title of the best rating shown when hovering over it with the cursor
ratePage-prompt: Prompt encouraging the user to vote, so that they can see the results
ratePage-error-category: Tracking category name for pages with invalid RatePage widgets
ratePage-missing-argument-page: Error message for the embeddable rating widget
ratePage-page-does-not-exist: Error message for the embeddable rating widget
ratePage-contest-id-too-long: Error message for the embeddable rating widget
ratePage-contest-id-invalid: Error message for the embeddable rating widget
ratePage-contest-disabled:
Status label for use in a summarized view of all contests
{{Identical|Disabled}}
ratePage-contest-enabled: Status label for use in a summarized view of all contests
ratePage-contests-list-enabled:
Table header label for use in a summarized view of all contests
{{identical|Status}}
ratePage-contests-list-id: Table header label for use in a summarized view of all contests
ratePage-contests-list-description:
Table header label for use in a summarized view of all contests
{{identical|Description}}
ratePage-contest-edit-title: Special page title in contest editing mode
ratePage-edit-contest-sub: Label under special page title. $1 – contest identifier
ratePage-contest-home:
Title of a link taking the user to the overview of all contests
{{identical|Home}}
ratePage-contests-new: Title of a button for creating a new contest
ratePage-results-list-ans: Contest results table header label. $1 is the rating value (typically 1–5).
ratePage-edit-done: Success message. $1 is the contest's identifier.
ratePage-log-contest-formatter: Fragment of a log entry specifying the contest's identifier. $1 is the identifier.
ratePage-no-such-contest: Error message. $1 is the contest's identifier.
ratePage-page-cannot-vote: Notice for users displayed in the rating widget for a page (not in a contest).
ratePage-vote-cannot-vote: Notice for users displayed in the rating widget.
ratePage-vote-cannot-see: Notice for users displayed in the rating widget.
ratepagecontests: Special page full title to be used on [[Special:SpecialPages]]
ratePage-deleted-page: Substitute text for deleted pages in contest results view
ratepage-contests-invalid-path: Requested action is invalid error message.
ratePage-page-cannot-be-rated: Embeddable widget error message. $1 – full name of the target article
